headline: Three Reasons to Avoid WSM and One Stock to Buy Instead
summary: Williams-Sonoma currently trades at $197 and has been a dream stock for shareholders. It’s returned 461% since December 2019, blowing past the S&P 500’s 89.1% gain. The company has also beaten the index over the past six months as its stock price is up 29.1% thanks to its solid quarterly results.
